cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.GT, cs.DS

This paper deals with resource allocation and sharing in mobile edge clouds, which is a topic related to computer networks and distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves game theory and optimization, which are relevant to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper discusses cooperative behavior among service providers, which is related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
